name: BigInt64Array.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 8 in the case of BigInt64Array.

name: BigInt64Array.prototype.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 8 in the case of a BigInt64Array.

name: BigInt64Array.prototype.constructor
description: The constructor function that created the instance object. For BigInt64Array instances, the initial value is the BigInt64Array constructor.
